<ul><li style="">Gears of War Ultimate (remake of the first game)</li><li style="">Lego Movie</li></ul><br />
1TB Bundles<br />
<ul><li style="">Tomb Raider</li><li style="">Fallout 4</li><li style="">Forza</li><li style="">Madden</li><li style="">Fifa</li><li style="">Holiday (Gears of War + Ori + Rare Replay)</li><li style="">Master Chief Collection (Halo 1-4 + ODST?)</li></ul><br />
